### Flex

A CSS flex container. Uses triple-colon.

```
:::flex[12px|center|flex-start|wrap]{
::badge[Python|#3b82f6]
||
::badge[NASM|#f59e0b]
||
::badge[Flask|#22c55e]
}
```

- **`[gap|align-items|justify-content|flex-wrap]`** — all optional, pipe-separated
- **`{item0||item1||…}`** — flex items

#### Preview

